data.text:
Stephen I de Blois King of England

Stephen I de Blois King of was born about 1097 in Blois, Loir-et-Cher, Orleanais/Centre, France. He died on October 25th, 1154 in Dover, Kent, England. He was buried in Count of Blois.

Matilda Countess of Boulogne

Matilda Countess of was born about 1105 in Boulogne-sur-Mer, Pas-de-Calais, France. She died on May 3rd, 1152 in Hedingham Castle, Kent, England.

Eustace IV Count of Boulogne

Eustace IV Count of was born about 1120 in Blois, Loir-et-Cher, Orleanais/Centre, France. He died on August 10th, 1153 in Boulogne-sur-Mer, Pas-de-Calais, France (dvp).

Mary de Blois , Abbess

Mary de was born in 1136 in Blois, Loir-et-Cher, Orleanais/Centre, France. She died at the age of 46 in 1182 in St. Austrebert, Eure-et-Loir, Beauce/Centre, France.
